sp {test*production*2
(state <s> ^level1.go true)
(<s> ^superstate.operator.name test1)
(<s> ^level1 <s1>)
-->
(<s1> ^touched-by p2)
(write (crlf) |S2: P2-2->S1| (crlf))
}

